WEBVTT

00:04.983 --> 00:06.749
You disapprove of me.

00:06.749 --> 00:09.868
You know, I'd stake out a little
distance from that Shore guy, Sally.

00:09.868 --> 00:12.791
He tends to leave people's minds
a little worse off than he finds them.

00:12.791 --> 00:15.991
Why are you counseling Sally
to distance herself from me?

00:15.991 --> 00:17.485
There are happily ever after guys,

00:17.485 --> 00:20.245
and there are those
who leave girls in a heap.

00:20.245 --> 00:21.582
And I can tell the difference.

00:21.582 --> 00:24.188
Sorry, I'm late, good people.

00:30.761 --> 00:33.347
Edwin, everything all right?

00:33.347 --> 00:34.572
Hunky dory.

00:34.572 --> 00:38.739
Denny, guess what, I'm due 
in court with Tara.

00:38.739 --> 00:39.784
We're on it.

00:39.784 --> 00:40.765
Don't you worry.

00:40.765 --> 00:42.879
–You just get better.
–Okay.

00:42.879 --> 00:44.912
Demagnetize his parking pass.

00:44.912 --> 00:47.395
–I beg your pardon?
–I know when the man is gone.

